{"tid":1358094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《壹週》：親中人士接指令暴力懲戒示威者　冀立功可當下屆司局長","createTime":"2019-07-24T00:53:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:23:06.000Z","uid":212626,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f48fa0f08c6218f4ecc6a8d4d94a4a0dc1151175","tid":1358094,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:53:32.000Z","msg":"本周日（21日）晚有大批白衣人闖入元朗西鐵站襲擊市民，造成數十人受傷。《壹週刊》引述消息稱，今次事件源起是有親中人士接下「阿爺」指令，期望完成後指令後，可提升自己在建制陣營中的地位，甚至可當上下屆政府司局長。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，由於「阿爺」下令要以暴力懲戒反送中示威者，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名親中人士為顯示自己的實力和決心，便接下指令，與多名有黑幫背景的鄉紳策動今次襲擊，「號召古惑仔執行私刑」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n報道續指，該名親中人士希望幫「阿爺」完成此事後，可以提升自己在建制陣營中的地位，或成為建制陣營「大佬」，甚至認為自己立功，便有機會在下屆政府當局長或司長。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/281640/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F281640%2F&d=gHNHb7VIn83nczLIzOZu1V3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=8aa83468\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/281640/</a>"},{"pid":"f64d37acc2a64bc3c3b15311ed82559378351209","tid":1358094,"uid":212626,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:54:23.000Z","msg":"消息人士<br />\n可信性自行評估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2691fed3d03543cf21f7171f6bcae811b15c7fea","tid":1358094,"uid":1166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:56:10.000Z","msg":"咪撚再post 852"},{"pid":"38de57b825fb10caf30d55592fa7bb7a3acec901","tid":1358094,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2691fed3d03543cf21f7171f6bcae811b15c7fea","tid":1358094,"uid":1166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:56:10.000Z","msg":"咪撚再post 852"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:59:34.000Z","msg":"852都有問題？"},{"pid":"65fdef56b4bc1ae38895e95d612b4eb157cbb3a5","tid":1358094,"uid":8441,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"38de57b825fb10caf30d55592fa7bb7a3acec901","tid":1358094,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2691